result.name: ukti-gpc-spend-over-500-pounds
result.notes: UKTI has published all Government Procurement Card (GPC) spend for Departmental GPC's. The data published includes transactions that have a single transaction value of £500 or above. This data will be published on a quarterly basis.

odi-certificate.title: UKTI Government Procurement Card spend - transactions over £500

organization.name: uk-trade-and-investment
organization.title: UK Trade and Investment
organization.description:
UKTI works with UK based businesses to ensure their success in international markets through exports. We encourage and support overseas companies to look at the UK as the best place to set up or expand their business.

http://www.gov.uk/ukti
